title: Purina Fancy Feast Grilled Wet Cat Food Tuna Feast in Wet Cat Food Gravy - (Pack of 24) 3 oz. Cans
description: Appease your cat's wish for delectable ocean-caught taste when you open a can of Purina Fancy Feast Grilled Tuna Feast in Gravy wet cat food. Made with responsibly sourced ingredients, this wet cat food contains tender cuts of grilled tuna, which are slow-cooked to perfection giving her the texture she craves, while the savory gravy enhances the taste she loves. She's getting her heart's desire along with the good food her body needs. The basted flavor of the gravy gives her delectable taste and lets the tuna flavor shine through, keeping her coming back for more each time you grab a can. Proper nutrition is important to you, and this gourmet Fancy Feast wet cat food provides 100 percent complete and balanced nutrition for cats from just-weaned kittens to full-grown adults. Essential vitamins and minerals found in each serving help support her whole-body heath, keeping her happy, healthy and assured of your love. Care for both her needs and her wants every day you fill her bowl.
